  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Banana Pop</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContainer\"><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wilson Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wilson_Portrait.png/20px-Wilson_Portrait.png?ecb2be\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>No, not brain freeze! I need that for science!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilson\" title=\"Wilson\">Wilson</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Willow Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Willow_Portrait.png/20px-Willow_Portrait.png?d73042\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>This is the opposite of burning.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Willow\" title=\"Willow\">Willow</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wolfgang Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wolfgang_Portrait.png/20px-Wolfgang_Portrait.png?62f11b\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Wolfgang can eat in one bite!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wolfgang\" title=\"Wolfgang\">Wolfgang</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab DSWHoverTabDefault\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wendy Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wendy_Portrait.png/20px-Wendy_Portrait.png?de6a98\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>I used to eat these with Abigail...</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wendy\" title=\"Wendy\">Wendy</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"WX-78 Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/WX-78_Portrait.png/20px-WX-78_Portrait.png?3d4137\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>STICK ADDON INSTALLED</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/WX-78\" title=\"WX-78\">WX-78</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wickerbottom Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wickerbottom_Portrait.png/20px-Wickerbottom_Portrait.png?8c0f1f\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Well, isn&#x27;t that refreshing?</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wickerbottom\" title=\"Wickerbottom\">Wickerbottom</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Woodie Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Woodie_Portrait.png/20px-Woodie_Portrait.png?247113\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>I&#x27;d prefer maple taffy...</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Woodie\" title=\"Woodie\">Woodie</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Maxwell Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Maxwell_Portrait.png/20px-Maxwell_Portrait.png?951b13\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Hm... I don&#x27;t know what I was expecting.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Maxwell\" title=\"Maxwell\">Maxwell</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wagstaff Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wagstaff_Portrait.png/20px-Wagstaff_Portrait.png?b5b749\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Quite efficient in lowering my internal temperature. Tastes good too.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wagstaff\" title=\"Wagstaff\">Wagstaff</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wigfrid Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wigfrid_Portrait.png/20px-Wigfrid_Portrait.png?a0e6fa\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>I&#x27;ve sömehöw föund a way tö make it even LESS appealing!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wigfrid\" title=\"Wigfrid\">Wigfrid</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Webber Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Webber_Portrait.png/20px-Webber_Portrait.png?dd96ec\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Yaaay! Popsicle, popsicle!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Webber\" title=\"Webber\">Webber</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Walani Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Walani_Portrait.png/20px-Walani_Portrait.png?4f4bad\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>The best way to keep cool. And very little preparation!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Walani\" title=\"Walani\">Walani</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Warly Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Warly_Portrait.png/20px-Warly_Portrait.png?842d5e\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Perhaps not my most complicated dish, but no less tasty.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Warly\" title=\"Warly\">Warly</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wilbur Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wilbur_Portrait.png/20px-Wilbur_Portrait.png?21e153\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>&#x27;Nonos!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilbur\" title=\"Wilbur\">Wilbur</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Woodlegs Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Woodlegs_Portrait.png/20px-Woodlegs_Portrait.png?73adea\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>I heard ther be gold in th&#x27;banana stand.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Woodlegs\" title=\"Woodlegs\">Woodlegs</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wilba Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wilba_Portrait.png/20px-Wilba_Portrait.png?a5c738\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>&#x27;TIS A NUMMIES&#x27;</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilba\" title=\"Wilba\">Wilba</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wormwood Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wormwood_Portrait.png/20px-Wormwood_Portrait.png?d47f44\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Frozen friend hair</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wormwood\" title=\"Wormwood\">Wormwood</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wheeler Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wheeler_Portrait.png/20px-Wheeler_Portrait.png?572eb9\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Banana. Stick. Ice. What more do you need?</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wheeler\" title=\"Wheeler\">Wheeler</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Winona Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Winona_Portrait.png/20px-Winona_Portrait.png?de0e5f\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Cool and refreshin&#x27;!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winona\" title=\"Winona\">Winona</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wortox Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wortox_Portrait.png/20px-Wortox_Portrait.png?cd0894\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Hyuyu, what will the mortals think of next.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wortox\" title=\"Wortox\">Wortox</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wurt Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wurt_Portrait.png/20px-Wurt_Portrait.png?dd6fd3\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Fruit taste even better on stick!</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wurt\" title=\"Wurt\">Wurt</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Walter Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Walter_Portrait.png/20px-Walter_Portrait.png?4ca0a0\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>Those are for little kids. But bananas are healthy so I guess it&#x27;s alright.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Walter\" title=\"Walter\">Walter</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"DSWHoverTab\">\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabSelector\"><img alt=\"Wanda Portrait.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wanda_Portrait.png/20px-Wanda_Portrait.png?201f9c\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></div>\n<div class=\"DSWHoverTabContent\"> \n<div><b>“</b><span>There&#x27;s nothing quicker and simpler than fruit on a stick.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wanda\" title=\"Wanda\">Wanda</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<p><b>Banana Pop</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> recipe introduced in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC. It is made from 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana\" title=\"Banana\">Raw Banana</a>, 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\">Ice</a>, and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\">Twig</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dorsal_Fin\" title=\"Dorsal Fin\">Dorsal Fin</a>. It is a great <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\">Sanity</a> restoring food, as Ice can be plentiful from refining <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hail\" title=\"Hail\">Hail</a> during the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hurricane_Season\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hurricane Season\">Hurricane Season</a> or using an <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Maker_3000\" title=\"Ice Maker 3000\">Ice Maker 3000</a>.\n</p><p>Its cooking ingredients cannot contain any kind of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fish</a>. Adding <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wobster\" title=\"Wobster\">Wobster</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shark_Fin\" title=\"Shark Fin\">Shark Fin</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Jellyfish\" title=\"Jellyfish\">Jellyfish</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\">Fishes</a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meats\">Meats</a> will result in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lobster_Bisque\" title=\"Lobster Bisque\">Lobster Bisque</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shark_Fin_Soup\" title=\"Shark Fin Soup\">Shark Fin Soup</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Jelly-O_Pop\" title=\"Jelly-O Pop\">Jelly-O Pop</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishsticks\" title=\"Fishsticks\">Fishsticks</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kabobs\" title=\"Kabobs\">Kabobs</a> respectively.\n</p><p>It restores 20 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/20px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, 12.5 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/20px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, and 33 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/20px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, and reduces body temperature by 1 degree per second for 10 seconds. \n</p><p>As a non-meat item, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wigfrid\" title=\"Wigfrid\">Wigfrid</a> cannot eat it.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana\" title=\"Banana\"><img alt=\"Banana SW.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Banana_SW.png?9085a0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires:<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Twigs.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Meats_Crock_Pot.png?bb1767\" width=\"580\" height=\"108\"></a></li>\n<li>Excludes: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Fishes_Crock_Pot.png?7aa195\" width=\"525\" height=\"110\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana_SW\" title=\"Banana SW\"><img alt=\"Banana SW.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Banana_SW.png?9085a0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana_Pop\" title=\"Banana Pop\"><img alt=\"Banana Pop.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Banana_Pop.png?aedde4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Banana_SW\" title=\"Banana SW\"><img alt=\"Banana SW.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Banana_SW.png?9085a0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dorsal_Fin\" title=\"Dorsal Fin\"><img alt=\"Dorsal Fin.png\" src=\